[Location]

What is ‘Safe Drop’?
A ‘Safe Drop’ is when our delivery driver finds a suitable place at your address where they can safely leave an item that does not require a signature.

If you are unable to locate the parcel, you may contact the sender to discuss alternative arrangements. Please provide them case number {!Case.CaseNumber} as a record of your enquiry.

To find out more about our delivery options and choose the best one for you, visit: auspost.com.au/delivery-options

Thanks for providing us feedback so we can continue to improve your delivery experience.

